## Verification Queries

```sql
-- Row count
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM tbl_items WHERE collection_type_id = 2;

-- Format distribution
SELECT format_name, COUNT(*)
FROM tbl_book_copies
JOIN lkup_book_format_details USING (format_detail_id)
GROUP BY format_name;

-- Reading status distribution
SELECT status_name, COUNT(*)
FROM tbl_items
JOIN lkup_book_read_statuses ON reading_status_id = read_status_id
WHERE collection_type_id = 2
GROUP BY status_name;

-- Top freeform tags
SELECT tag_name, COUNT(*)
FROM xref_book_item_tags
JOIN lkup_book_tags USING (tag_id)
GROUP BY tag_name
ORDER BY 2 DESC
LIMIT 20;
```

Spot-check 5‚Äì10 individual books against the Goodreads source, then re-run the script to confirm 0 new imports (idempotency).
